btrplace.solver.choco.view

Class DefaultAliasedCumulatives

  • java.lang.Object
    • btrplace.solver.choco.view.AbstractCumulatives
      • btrplace.solver.choco.view.DefaultAliasedCumulatives
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AliasedCumulatives, ChocoView

    public class DefaultAliasedCumulatives
extends AbstractCumulatives
implements AliasedCumulatives
    Builder to create constraints where slices have to be placed on nodes with regards to the slice and the nodes capacity.

    It differs from DefaultCumulatives as a resource may in fact be an alias to another one. This allows to create a fake resource that aggregate the capacity of each of the aliased resources.

    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
